3 Tier architecture is as follows 
++++++++++++++++++++++++++

DB layer: Percona DB is deployed with a common mount volume in the server.
 App Layer : Both applications running on Python, app1, and app2  are  connected to the common DB 
Web Layer or Loadbalancer layer: Ngnix load balancer will act as the ingress controller and will route the traffic uniformly among the applications connected to it.
